dges":["Merker"],"To add trust badges, you can manage them in":["For \u00e5 legge til tillitsmerker kan du administrere dem i"],"trust badges settings":["innstillinger for tillitsmerker"],"Priority":["Prioritet"],"Review Badges":["Vurderingsmerker"],"Footer Text":["Bunntekst"],"The settings in this editor cover the most commonly used options for most stores. However, many additional settings are available. Once you\\'ve saved any changes, head over to the CheckoutWC menu in your WordPress dashboard to explore more options.":["Innstillingene i denne editoren dekker de mest brukte alternativene for de fleste butikker. Det finnes imidlertid mange flere innstillinger tilgjengelig. N\u00e5r du har lagret endringer, g\u00e5 til CheckoutWC-menyen i WordPress-dashbordet for \u00e5 utforske flere alternativer."]}}}